des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart fan. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “iPower Life” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “iPower Life” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “iPower” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “iPower” skill, and you'll be navigated to “iPower” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
“Alexa, turn off the fan.”
“Alexa, set the fan speed to 1.”
“Alexa, set the fan speed to maximum.”
“Alexa, turn up the fan speed.”
"Alexa, what is the fan speed?"
"Alexa, set the fan mode to timer.”
